					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7060165#post-3919169</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7060165/scp-4222#post-3919169</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 20 Aug 2018 17:17:21 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Mortos</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1705184</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This is top tier. I especially love the &quot;The SCUBA equipment was later found on an emperor penguin on the southern coast of Greenland.&quot; footnote. You've got some great pacing here, you start weird and just get weirder and weirder throughout while somehow remaining consistent and coherent, which is very impressive. Easy +1.</p> <p>Only problem I spotted was that this line -</p> <blockquote> <p>The point in time at which City Trust international bank went or became inside a tuna is the subject of ongoing investigation.</p> </blockquote> <p>- is very clunky. Recommend rewording to something like &quot;Investigations into how or when City Trust international bank began operating from inside a tuna are ongoing.&quot;</p> <p>Excellent stuff.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
