						 <p><em>Sell a man a fish, he eats for a day. Teach a man to fish, you ruin a wonderful business opportunity.</em></p> <p>Thanks so so much to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/maliceaforethought" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2902864&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1534984410" alt="MaliceAforethought" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2902864)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/maliceaforethought" >MaliceAforethought</a></span> for coming up with the idea for this and going over the mess that resulted, and to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1372582&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1534984410" alt="Jacob Conwell" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1372582)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" >Jacob Conwell</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3075960&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1534984411" alt="stormbreath" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3075960)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" >stormbreath</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lordstonefish" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2527320&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1534984411" alt="LordStonefish" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2527320)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lordstonefish" >LordStonefish</a></span> for more help. And also to everyone reading this.</p> <p>I have an <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/fieldstone-ao-file">author page</a> with more things.</p> <p>Edit: also thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/modern-erasmus" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3129691&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1534984411" alt="Modern_Erasmus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3129691)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/modern-erasmus" >Modern_Erasmus</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/adrian-godet" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3320927&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1534984411" alt="Adrian Godet" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3320927)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/adrian-godet" >Adrian Godet</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mr-brooks" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=448837&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1534984411" alt="Mr Brooks" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=448837)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mr-brooks" >Mr Brooks</a></span> for reviewing this in the forums! Multiple rounds of feedback really makes a huge difference.</p> <p>Image credits:<br /> Tuna public domain courtesy of the NOAA: [<a href="http://www.photolib.noaa.gov/htmls/fish2003.htm">http://www.photolib.noaa.gov/htmls/fish2003.htm</a>].<br /> Military dolphin public domain courtesy of US government, via wikipedia: [<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Military_dolphin">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Military_dolphin</a>].</p> 
